Package tiralabyra

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AStar
    Solve shortest paths using A* (or Dijkstra, when no heuristics specified).
    BreadthFirstSearch
    Solve paths through a connected graph using BFS.
    ConnectedGraph
    A graph of nodes connected by edges.
    Edge
    Represents an edge between two nodes in a graph, with weight.
    Image
    Represents a bitmap image of a labyrinth.
    MinHeap
    Minimum heap.
    Point
    A point in 2D space with integer coordinates.
    PrioNode
    A graph node that is comparable to other nodes by total distance traveled plus an estimate of the remaining path length.
    Queue
    FIFO queue of integers, using a circular buffer internally.
    SolvedResult
    Results of a labyrinth solve.
